The paper proposes a deep neural network with fuzzy reasoning rules for image classification, which falls under the intersection of machine learning, computer vision, and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves the integration of fuzzy systems, which is related to the sub-categories cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
